Patient Monitoring

* Blood Pressure (Systolic and Diastolic)
* Pulse Rate
* Breathing Rate (measure bpm)
* Temperature (measure at Celsius)
* Weight (measure at kg)
* Age + Height (const)

Each module needs to have a minimum and a maximum value that suit the patient

